('koshi-tappu-wildlife-reserve', 'Koshi Tappu Wildlife Reserve', 'Ramsar-listed wetland on Koshi River floodplain, home to endangered wild water buffalo (Arna) and 500+ bird species. Offers birdwatching, elephant safaris, and boat rides.', 'WILDLIFE', 8, 1, 'Koshi', 6, 'Sunsari', 26.65, 87.35, 90, 'EASY', 'WINTER', 2000, '4-6 hours', true, true, NOW()),
('baraha-kshetra', 'Baraha Kshetra', 'Sacred Hindu pilgrimage at Koshi-Saptakoshi confluence associated with Vishnu boar incarnation (Varaha). Features ancient shrines and hosts the massive Baraha Mela fair.', 'RELIGIOUS', 3, 1, 'Koshi', 6, 'Sunsari', 26.8833, 87.2, 100, 'EASY', 'WINTER', 0, '3-4 hours', false, false, NOW()),
('gadhimal-temple', 'Gadhimal Temple', 'Ancient Bara district temple dedicated to Goddess Gadhi Devi, known for Gadhi Mela festival and the legend of a princess self-immolation.', 'RELIGIOUS', 3, 2, 'Madhesh', 20, 'Bara', 27.05, 85.05, 85, 'EASY', 'WINTER', 0, '1-2 hours', false, false, NOW()),
('sankata-temple', 'Sankata Temple', 'Historic Janakpur temple to goddess Sankata (protection), featuring traditional Mithila architecture and serving local religious ceremonies.', 'RELIGIOUS', 3, 2, 'Madhesh', 16, 'Dhanusha', 26.726, 85.922, 78, 'EASY', 'WINTER', 0, '1-2 hours', false, false, NOW()),
('bishahari-temple-madhesh', 'Bishahari Temple', 'Parsa district temple dedicated to snake goddess Bishahari, believed to protect from snakebites. Surrounded by ancient banyan trees and sacred ponds.', 'RELIGIOUS', 3, 2, 'Madhesh', 21, 'Parsa', 27.0833, 84.8667, 95, 'EASY', 'WINTER', 0, '1-2 hours', false, false, NOW()),
('dakshinkali-temple', 'Dakshinkali Temple', 'One of Nepal''s most important Shakta temples dedicated to goddess Kali, 22 km south of Kathmandu. Famous for animal sacrifices, drawing thousands on Tuesdays and Saturdays.', 'RELIGIOUS', 3, 3, 'Bagmati', 27, 'Lalitpur', 27.55, 85.2833, 1350, 'EASY', 'SPRING', 100, '2-3 hours', true, false, NOW()),
('indreshwar-temple', 'Indreshwar Temple', 'Magnificent three-roofed pagoda Shiva temple in Panauti, finest example of Newari architecture at the Roshi-Punyamati rivers confluence.', 'RELIGIOUS', 3, 3, 'Bagmati', 25, 'Kavrepalanchok', 27.578, 85.52, 1430, 'EASY', 'SPRING', 0, '2-3 hours', false, true, NOW()),
('kalmochi-cave', 'Kalmochi Cave', 'Hidden Lalitpur cave temple with natural stalactites and ancient meditation chambers, believed used by Buddhist monks for centuries.', 'RELIGIOUS', 3, 3, 'Bagmati', 27, 'Lalitpur', 27.55, 85.35, 1450, 'MODERATE', 'SPRING', 50, '1-2 hours', false, false, NOW()),
('chandragiri-hill', 'Chandragiri Hill', 'Scenic hilltop south of Kathmandu accessible by cable car, offering panoramic Himalayan views from Annapurna to Everest. Features Bhaleshwor Temple at summit.', 'SCENIC', 9, 3, 'Bagmati', 27, 'Lalitpur', 27.56, 85.22, 2551, 'EASY', 'AUTUMN', 670, '3-4 hours', true, false, NOW()),
